Gracita Morales https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gracita_Morales 0 María Gracia Morales Carvajal (11 November 1928 – 3 April 1995) better known as Gracita Morales was a classic Spanish film supporting actress with a famous voice. She acted in many films as a maid.
